В качестве БД предпологается использовать postgres для обсепечени согласованости данных и атомарности.

Place:
id: uuid
name: str
address: str (or smth more complex, eg. to allow searching by city)
host: uuid (user id)
created_at: datetime


Watch:
id: uuid
host: uuid (user id)
filmwork: uuid
place: Place
time: datetime
seats: int
price: float (or decimal)
status: text (eg "created", "canceled", ...)
created_at: datetime


Reservation:
id: uuid
watch_id: uuid
participant_id: uuid
created_at: datetime
